title: Paulie Gee's
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, American, Pizza, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Hipster, casual vibe, urban barn decor pizzeria. Vegan pizza menu with ingredients like house-made vegan fennel sausage, house-made cashew ricotta cheese, Italian tomatoes, grilled leek, marinated baby kale, nutritional yeast, pickled red grape halves. Pizzas are baked inside a Neapolitan-style wood-burning brick oven.
